{"data":{"id":"ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc","rating":4.9,"websiteUri":"http://www.212hvac.com/","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":true,"periods":[{"open":{"day":1,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":1,"hour":23,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":2,"hour":23,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":3,"hour":23,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":4,"hour":23,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":5,"hour":23,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":6,"hour":8,"minute":0},"close":{"day":6,"hour":23,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"],"nextCloseTime":"2026-02-17T04:00:00Z"},"userRatingCount":323,"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCT1MzTlZVVmwxTlU1dGJtaHZkV2hYVG5GeGNVRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"8 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I had two units installed a bit over one year ago by a different company and one of the units developed a refrigerant leak. We called for service and Andrei C. came out to assist. He found that the leak was caused by poor installation and insulation by the original company and came back to repair it. The quality of work (fit and finish) of the new pipes and insulation was honestly done so much better than when it was originally installed. I would also like to mention even though we had an appointment for a later date and time, they called and came for the fix a few days sooner due to an available opening and saved us from a few extra days of heat and misery. Their workmanship is of good quality for sure. Their professionalism is also good, no doubt. Their pricing (4 stars) is a bit on the high side for me but at the end of the day, I guess you get what you pay for. Thanks Andrei (AC) and team. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I had two units installed a bit over one year ago by a different company and one of the units developed a refrigerant leak. We called for service and Andrei C. came out to assist. He found that the leak was caused by poor installation and insulation by the original company and came back to repair it. The quality of work (fit and finish) of the new pipes and insulation was honestly done so much better than when it was originally installed. I would also like to mention even though we had an appointment for a later date and time, they called and came for the fix a few days sooner due to an available opening and saved us from a few extra days of heat and misery. Their workmanship is of good quality for sure. Their professionalism is also good, no doubt. Their pricing (4 stars) is a bit on the high side for me but at the end of the day, I guess you get what you pay for. Thanks Andrei (AC) and team. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Fred","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109402450903294051192/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr_yfoy1cJnDZ2neO1wz1QDQ_3x4N_y17DmDQaWslGJGzq3jb4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-06-19T22:33:20.032945289Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCT1MzTlZVVmwxTlU1dGJtaHZkV2hYVG5GeGNVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xCT1MzTlZVVmwxTlU1dGJtaHZkV2hYVG5GeGNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c2595f953a325f:0xa7a86039d5636fdd"},{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdFlrTnpTelJDYlhoV1l6bFhhMGxEUkZCSVRFRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"We’ve been using 212 hvac for years, and they  consistently fix our issues, are reachable and  available in a pinch, punctual and responsive. They do great work and are good at explaining the issue/problem. Mykola was especially helpful today - Thanksgiving week, no less - in fixing a broken furnace issue.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"We’ve been using 212 hvac for years, and they  consistently fix our issues, are reachable and  available in a pinch, punctual and responsive. They do great work and are good at explaining the issue/problem. Mykola was especially helpful today - Thanksgiving week, no less - in fixing a broken furnace issue.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Elizabeth Moller","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107266935224403671316/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNVu2OgZPC9bzJFdQoheZCY4Bi_9bV135WrqhJ8En5unE39J3QUw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-11-25T01:30:10.529313968Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdFlrTnpTelJDYlhoV1l6bFhhMGxEUkZCSVRFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kdFlrTnpTelJDYlhoV1l6bFhhMGxEUkZCSVRFRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c2595f953a325f:0xa7a86039d5636fdd"},{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkWFRUSTFhM0pwWlRSa09TMU1NVTVNWDNKVlptYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"4 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"212 HVAC services our home heating and cooling system in spring and fall. Mykola the technician always does a great job, is efficient and friendly and tidy, and even showed me a trick about the mini-split vents that I didn't know about. Plus their annual maintenance plan pricing is very reasonable. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"212 HVAC services our home heating and cooling system in spring and fall. Mykola the technician always does a great job, is efficient and friendly and tidy, and even showed me a trick about the mini-split vents that I didn't know about. Plus their annual maintenance plan pricing is very reasonable. Highly recommend.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Caitlin Van Dusen","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111078763977249828904/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7GLEwNjWwPUMlTyNeBKy6mpAwZx6URclXwqaQCPwDxND3Phs_XQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2025-10-01T14:58:30.143342777Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkWFRUSTFhM0pwWlRSa09TMU1NVTVNWDNKVlptYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkWFRUSTFhM0pwWlRSa09TMU1NVTVNWDNKVlptYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c2595f953a325f:0xa7a86039d5636fdd"},{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wRk1VbEVhVzlUV2xOYU9XVkdNbkpVWlZCRFdIYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Nick did a great job servicing of the 4 air handler units in my apartment. He took his time going through everything properly and did not rush. He also explained how to better care for the units. The units are so incredibly clean compared to before.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Nick did a great job servicing of the 4 air handler units in my apartment. He took his time going through everything properly and did not rush. He also explained how to better care for the units. The units are so incredibly clean compared to before.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Aniqa Hassan","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116861089679516992731/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1jZNmVlTW_fccqA8JvoS08K3e_D1rnsJrfaShaXyRRRLuFEAk=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-11-19T17:29:58.923890007Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wRk1VbEVhVzlUV2xOYU9XVkdNbkpVWlZCRFdIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wRk1VbEVhVzlUV2xOYU9XVkdNbkpVWlZCRFdIYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c2595f953a325f:0xa7a86039d5636fdd"},{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkamRIZFJTMlJGTFRCT1JHNHhhME5TTmpkSVduYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":4,"text":{"text":"The service from Mykola was excellent. He was friendly, knowledgeable, clearly not rushing and even found a solution that ended up costing less by asking a simple question.\n\nMy only complaint is with the company itself. Their communication was not very good. They would end calls by telling me they’d call back in 2 hours or “tomorrow,” but they never did. I had to chase every time to keep things moving.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"The service from Mykola was excellent. He was friendly, knowledgeable, clearly not rushing and even found a solution that ended up costing less by asking a simple question.\n\nMy only complaint is with the company itself. Their communication was not very good. They would end calls by telling me they’d call back in 2 hours or “tomorrow,” but they never did. I had to chase every time to keep things moving.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Adam Bass","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118002505758834858345/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6o2tEDJfWO-FbDQBt0b4q_Hfckh74HUCl3dXGB5RC_zObSvW5=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-11-22T21:05:29.752166944Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkamRIZFJTMlJGTFRCT1JHNHhhME5TTmpkSVduYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkamRIZFJTMlJGTFRCT1JHNHhhME5TTmpkSVduYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c2595f953a325f:0xa7a86039d5636fdd"}],"photos":[{"name":"places/ChIJXzI6lV9ZwokR3W9j1TlgqKc/ph